Invocation Name: fidget spinner
des:
Fidget Spinner is the latest edition of fun game based on the popular stress relief toy. Choose your spinner and special ability. Alexa will spin the fidget and tell you the number of spins. 

If the number is high enough, you can unlock higher levels with new spinners and new abilities. The game has number of levels with dozens of different spinners and abilities to choose from.
